      <title>02 - Guiding Principles for Data Management</title>
      <link>https://seramirezruiz.github.io/data-science-for-policymaking/materials/day-6/2-data-management/</link>
      <pubDate>Mon, 27 May 2024 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
